Plot: Tells the story about the 7 signatories of the Proclamation of the 1916 Easter Rising, before, during & after the rising. P.H Pearse, James Connolly, Eamon Ceannt, Tom Clarke, Joseph Plunkett, Sean Mac Diarmada & Tomas MacDonagh.
Title: 1916 Seachtar na Cásca
Actors: Rory Mullen, Tadhg Murphy, Seán T. Ó Meallaigh, Stephen D'Arcy
